  {
    "name": "Linden Dance Academy",
    "website_url": "https://www.lindendanceacademy.com",
    "email": "danielle@lindendanceacademy.com",
    "phone": null,
    "address": "26 Season THE JOY OFMOVEMENTSIGN UPAbout UsOUR MISSIONOur mission is to provide excellent dance training in ballet, tap, jazz, hip-hop, lyrical, contemporary by encouraging our students of all ages and levels to reach their potential technically, as well as to help them develop confidence, responsibility, and self-discipline, and to teach the importance of team work and setting goals. CLASS QUALITYClass levels are based on ability not by age group. This allows each individual to progress to their full potential without frustration or stifle their talent. Limited class sizes ensure that each dancer receives proper and individualized attention. Our focus is giving our dancers a strong technical foundation in dance in which they can build upon each year to be to proficient in their desired dance discipline while maintaining an enthusiasm for performance.Whether it is the recreational student, or the serious dancer, everyone can feel like a star at Linden Dance Academy. All students are encouraged to set goals, work hard, and enjoy their own personal achievements. Our Christian based programs allow our students to learn experiment and test their dance knowledge through performances, both formal and informal, as well as create their own choreography or compete across the U.S.OPPORTUNITIESSummer Schedule 2025GalleryContact UsLinden Dance Academy15188 S Linden RoadLinden, Michigan 48451",
